      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions (fluid properties, rotational speed, flow rate) match COU operating envelope within stated uncertainty bounds.",
      "rationale": "Test conditions match COU at three of five operating points; two high-speed points were not replicated in the validation experiment due to rig limitations. Achieved level 3 is below required level 4."
    },
