      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments performed on the identical pump geometry under identical fluid and operating conditions as the COU.",
      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA benchmark pump geometry, which matches the COU geometry, but the working fluid in validation experiments was saline-RBC suspension rather than the patient blood analog specified in the COU. Achieved level 3 is below required level 5."
