      "acceptanceCriteria": "Full sensitivity analysis and uncertainty propagation for all model input parameters including blood viscosity, pump geometry tolerances, and boundary conditions.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was initiated but input parameter distributions for blood viscosity and geometric tolerances are not fully characterized. Input uncertainty assessment is flagged as an epistemic gap."
