      "acceptanceCriteria": "Statistical characterization of biological variability in RBC fragility across the test sample population with at least n=10 donors.",
      "rationale": "Experimental hemolysis measurements were performed with a single pooled blood sample. Inter-donor variability in RBC fragility was not characterized. Test sample assessment is flagged as an epistemic gap."
